#: .\antifungal_ants.json
msgid "antifungal ant"
msgid_plural "antifungal ants"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'antifungal ant'}
#: .\antifungal_ants.json
msgid ""
"An enormous green ant covered in chitinous plates.  It possesses a pair of "
"wriggling antennae and vicious-looking mandibles. It seems to emit "
"fungicide."
msgstr ""

#: .\antifungal_ants.json
msgid "antifungal larva"
msgid_plural "antifungal larvas"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'antifungal larva'}
#: .\antifungal_ants.json
msgid ""
"A pulsating sausage of glistening white flesh, the size of a large cat.  On "
"one end is a set of squirming mouth parts."
msgstr ""

#: .\antifungal_ants.json
msgid "antifungal queen"
msgid_plural "antifungal queens"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'antifungal queen'}
#: .\antifungal_ants.json
msgid ""
"A colossal green ant with a bulging, bloated thorax.  It moves slowly and "
"deliberately, tending to nearby eggs and continually laying more. Much like "
"it's minions, it emits antifungal clouds."
msgstr ""

#: .\antifungal_ants.json .\extend.json
msgid "soldier ant"
msgid_plural "soldier ants"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'soldier ant'}
#: .\antifungal_ants.json
msgid ""
"A huge and hairy green ant almost twice the size of other giant ants.  "
"Bulging pincers extend from its jaws. It emits clouds of strong fungicide to"
" protect the queen."
msgstr ""

#: .\bug_professions.json
msgctxt "profession_male"
msgid "Antagonizer Fanatic"
msgstr ""

#: .\bug_professions.json
msgctxt "profession_female"
msgid "Antagonizer Fanatic"
msgstr ""

#. ~ Profession (male Antagonizer Fanatic) description
#: .\bug_professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_male"
msgid ""
"As a kid, you were a fan of the Grognak the Barbarian comics, and "
"specifically their villain, the AntAgonizer. In the chaos of the Cataclysm, "
"you managed to save your ant farm, costume, and favorite comic."
msgstr ""

#. ~ Profession (female Antagonizer Fanatic) description
#: .\bug_professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_female"
msgid ""
"As a kid, you were a fan of the Grognak the Barbarian comics, and "
"specifically their villain, the AntAgonizer. In the chaos of the Cataclysm, "
"you managed to save your ant farm, costume, and favorite comic."
msgstr ""

#: .\bug_professions.json
msgctxt "profession_male"
msgid "Ant nerd"
msgstr ""

#: .\bug_professions.json
msgctxt "profession_female"
msgid "Ant nerd"
msgstr ""

#. ~ Profession (male Ant nerd) description
#: .\bug_professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_male"
msgid ""
"Your ants were your best friends for your life. Now theyre your only "
"friends. At least nobody will bully you now... Also, your colony provided "
"you a weird egg before the end times."
msgstr ""

#. ~ Profession (female Ant nerd) description
#: .\bug_professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_female"
msgid ""
"Your ants were your best friends for your life. Now theyre your only "
"friends. At least nobody will bully you now... Also, your colony provided "
"you a weird egg before the end times."
msgstr ""

#: .\bug_professions.json
msgctxt "profession_male"
msgid "Ant maniac"
msgstr ""

#: .\bug_professions.json
msgctxt "profession_female"
msgid "Ant maniac"
msgstr ""

#. ~ Profession (male Ant maniac) description
#: .\bug_professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_male"
msgid ""
"Before the cataclysm, you were an avid antkeeper, and kept a very dangerous "
"breed. So dangerous, you had to wear protective gear in the ant room. You "
"found a mysterious, large egg in there shortly before the cataclysm. Lets "
"hope it can save you now."
msgstr ""

#. ~ Profession (female Ant maniac) description
#: .\bug_professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_female"
msgid ""
"Before the cataclysm, you were an avid antkeeper, and kept a very dangerous "
"breed. So dangerous, you had to wear protective gear in the ant room. You "
"found a mysterious, large egg in there shortly before the cataclysm. Lets "
"hope it can save you now."
msgstr ""

#: .\bug_professions.json
msgctxt "profession_male"
msgid "Ant Researcher"
msgstr ""

#: .\bug_professions.json
msgctxt "profession_female"
msgid "Ant Researcher"
msgstr ""

#. ~ Profession (male Ant Researcher) description
#: .\bug_professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_male"
msgid ""
"Before the cataclysm, you were trying to make a breed of ants that could "
"resist the cordyceps fungus. You had just succeeded when your undead co-"
"worker spilled something on your ant tray."
msgstr ""

#. ~ Profession (female Ant Researcher) description
#: .\bug_professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_female"
msgid ""
"Before the cataclysm, you were trying to make a breed of ants that could "
"resist the cordyceps fungus. You had just succeeded when your undead co-"
"worker spilled something on your ant tray."
msgstr ""

